Description: IOM1 Type of usage of AI11.0 / None /nonE: No function1 / Target Velocity /SPdS: Target velocity forthe velocity controller2 / Target Torque /trqS: Target torque for thecurrent controller3 / Velocity Limitation /LSPd: Limitation of thereference velocity for the velocity controller4 / Current Limitation /Lcur: Limitation of thereference current for the current controllerSetting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active the next time thepower stage is enabled.Available with firmware version ≥V01.06.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 304F:EhModbus 20252Profibus 20252CIP 179.1.14ModbusTCP 20252EtherCAT 304F:EhPROFINET 20252
